/> <br />\n最近又拒絕一次 佢好似終於開始死心係private ig屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bd05c1b21ba178f89d7330c03ed9ec258fd5264","tid":246531,"uid":93655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:41:09.000Z","msg":"最後散左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ecbe9d036bb0f55d2e3ed3aeea9b93c062b120c","tid":246531,"uid":10242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:41:43.000Z","msg":"無數次經驗 <br />\n拒絕/唔答 通常都連朋友都無得做"},{"pid":"cd5ce97902ef65a1bf6282e7785eb7cedc9f3c3d","tid":246531,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T14:43:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個女仔鍾意左我6年 對我表白過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近又拒絕一次 佢好似終於開始死心係private ig屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n6年真係一d感覺都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d54d4a3815d635d3b5a34c0b924fde59c0411cf","tid":246531,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:02:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有個女仔鍾意左我6年 對我表白過幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近又拒絕一次 佢好似終於開始死心係private ig屌鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實無論男女都好 冇感覺就係冇感覺 試過一次表白唔Work就走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bbab04f0337e804516215d965439212c9c0b768","tid":246531,"uid":34880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"利申 巴打<br />\n我嗰陣f.5 佢f.3 暑假準備升f.6 , f.4嗰陣開始<br />\n我同佢唔好彩喺唔啱嘅時間識到 對的人 錯的時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱嗰段時間我忙緊一樣好重要嘅事 <br />\n根本分唔到身去拍拖 畀唔到時間同佢相處咁多（面對面）<br />\n<br />\n本身我地whatsapp得好密 每日由朝傾到晚 由講早晨講到唔捨得瞓 但我諗通之後決定開始唔覆佢機<br />\n就算佢同我講埋生日快樂 聖誕快樂 想送禮物畀我（親手整咗好耐）但我都冇覆佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n終於有一日佢都放棄咗 冇再搵我<br />\n<br />\n點解當時我要咁做？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為我覺得既然我唔能夠擺晒副心機同佢一齊 我冇謂格硬同佢一齊 喺嗰段時間我根本分唔到身同佢一齊 費事拖累佢同時令我對佢唔夠好又做唔成我忙緊嗰件事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢到畀機會我向妳講返聲我一路唔敢講嘅對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但完咗件事之後我就一直好後悔 好遺憾 好慚愧<br />\n我唔知會對妳傷害究竟有幾深 因為妳係我第一個想發展嘅女仔 但我嗰陣唔識處理 結果我選擇咗逃避妳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但之後聽d friend講妳搵咗另一個男仔拍拖 我個心先好過少少 <br />\n我到宜家其實都有d放唔低妳 同其他女仔傾計嘅時候都成日諗返起妳<br />\n但我平時見到妳po ig都唔敢like 怕妳再諗起我 諗起d唔開心嘅回憶<br />\n對唔住<br />\n我宜家都仲未好有勇氣發展新一段關係<br />\n<br />\n識得勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n求巴絲屌下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"422c7f9eb7f06920f1bb2d689f797b2f360ac2b0","tid":246531,"uid":34880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:05:43.000Z","msg":"有d長 sorry巴絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab92a7e400db4e507f2d575d1a4f05f0df702e7d","tid":246531,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前同你講咗 但見你冇反應<br />\n所以都知道你嘅答案 但我都想繼續做返朋友 我諗你都係<br />\n之後我開始隔好耐先覆你 或者係一日先講得一次嘢<br />\n咁係因為唔想你覺得chur 同埋 其實自己想減退對你嘅好感，忘記你<br />\n<br />\n開呢個po嘅原因其實想話你知 雖然我覆少咗但我仍然都想同你做朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係只係朋友 冇其他<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8852d8e60e0a7eb09d9ed10921715dd61e32760","tid":246531,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T15:10:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都好想<span style=\"font-size: xx-large